    <item>
      <title>沙特阿美启动巨额股票出售，以测试投资者兴趣</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/aramco-kicks-off-giant-share-sale-in-test-of-investor-appetite</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿美公司周日开始出售股票，为沙特阿拉伯筹集约 120 亿美元，这是近年来最大的交易之一，将考验投资者对沙特阿拉伯资产的兴趣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/aramco-kicks-off-giant-share-sale-in-test-of-investor-appetite</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国金融监督院警告新税法将导致本地股票资金外流</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/south-korea-s-fss-warns-of-outflows-from-local-stocks-on-new-tax</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国最高金融监管机构警告称，如果明年按计划引入资本利得税，散户投资者可能会逃离本土股市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/south-korea-s-fss-warns-of-outflows-from-local-stocks-on-new-tax</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 03:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行首次降息将使世界利率路径出现分化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/central-banks-latest-world-rate-paths-set-to-diverge-with-ecb-s-first-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行周四将进行本周期首次降息，此举可能为欧元贬值打开大门，因此该地区的政策路径与美国出现分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/central-banks-latest-world-rate-paths-set-to-diverge-with-ecb-s-first-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>智利总统加布里埃尔·博里奇提出堕胎和安乐死合法化计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/chile-s-boric-lays-out-plans-to-legalize-abortion-and-euthanasia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利总统加布里埃尔·博里奇表示，他将提出一项彻底合法化堕胎的法案，并将加速对安乐死提案的辩论，这两项计划在分裂的国会中都面临着艰难的批准战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/chile-s-boric-lays-out-plans-to-legalize-abortion-and-euthanasia</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 19:22:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>《信贷周刊》：贷款狂潮掩盖了违约损失的增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/loan-frenzy-masks-rising-losses-on-defaults-credit-weekly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上个月，企业利用现金追逐信贷的机会，出售了创纪录数量的杠杆贷款。然而，从违约的回收率来看，这类债务的风险正在不断增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/loan-frenzy-masks-rising-losses-on-defaults-credit-weekly</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>未经测试的 ETF 被推销给投资者以对冲全球混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/untested-etfs-pitched-to-investors-as-hedge-against-global-chaos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中东和欧洲的战争、中美紧张局势、气候变化、新技术带来的威胁——地缘政治风险无处不在。一群基金经理正在推销一类 ETF，声称可以为所有这些不确定性提供对冲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/untested-etfs-pitched-to-investors-as-hedge-against-global-chaos</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 17:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
