      <title>德国大面积洪灾致跨境运输中断</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/widespread-flooding-disrupts-cross-border-transport-in-germany</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国南部和瑞士部分地区的强降雨导致交通和通讯严重中断，周末雷暴天气将进一步加剧。]]></description>
